{
  "texts": [
    "Often, there is a disconnect between where computations and data are processed (e.g., computational notebooks on servers) and where visualizations are viewed, resulting in disjointed workflow components and a complex process.",
    "Bridging the gap in this sensemaking process [74] could enable users to author more effective representations with greater efficiency. 5.",
    "Support Collaborative Authoring.",
    "Receiving feedback is an integral part of the authoring workflows of genomics experts.",
    "Furthermore, genomics visualization authors collaborate by exchanging pieces of code."
  ]
}